There are dozens of tickets with problems when updating to 3.5 from a previous version when using LDAP. Those problems are solved by upgrading to 4.0.5.

4.x [upgrade manuals|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Upgrading+Confluence+Manually] says:
{quote}
Upgrading from Confluence 3.4 or earlier?

Please upgrade to Confluence 3.5 before upgrading to Confluence 4.x.
{quote}

I think we should add a note mentioning that users using LDAP should upgrade directly to 4.0.5 rather than 3.5.

